N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5305.3 - Duration of registration

State Regulations
(a) Gaming employee registrations shall remain valid as set forth in Racing, Pari-Mutuel Wagering and Breeding Law section 1325(6). (b) Each gaming employee registration shall
indicate an expiration date. Notes
